ld. Finally, numerical results\nare presented which demonstrate the performance gains of the proposed hybrid\nIRS architecture and its optimal design over the conventional schemes with\nactive/passive IRS only under various practical system setups.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2022 08:05:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 5 Jul 2022 02:17:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-06"}
