 \\mathcal{T}$, thus\nproving the consistency of the proposed methods in terms of the grid size\n$|\\mathcal{T}|$. We complement our theoretical findings with experiments on\nsynthetic and real data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2022 14:45:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Jul 2022 14:25:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-18"}
