 clustering amplitude, but by background modifications to\nthe late-time expansion rate due to massive neutrinos, which worsen the fit to\nmeasurements of the BAO scale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 4 Jul 2022 15:22:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Jul 2022 12:59:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 26 Jan 2023 13:33:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-20"}
